	<li id="menu-item-232611" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/read-smart/">Read Smart</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-232430" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/talk-easy/">Talk Easy</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-174862" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/tor-presents-voyage-into-genre/">Tor Presents: Voyage Into Genre</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-220836" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/windham-campbell-prizes-podcast/">Windham-Campbell Prizes Podcast</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-232431" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/write-minded/">Write-minded</a></li>

